  "notes": "Captured 2026-04 Shopify behavior for public `constraintsUpdates` on `metafieldDefinitionUpdate`: setting constraint values, enforcing the constrained-definition pin guard, deleting and creating values, clearing constraints with `key: null, values: []`, and pinning after unconstrain. Live 2026-04 introspection rejects legacy `constraints` and `constraintsSet` on `MetafieldDefinitionUpdateInput`, so those internal legacy branches are covered by runtime tests rather than this public Admin API capture."
